  description: "pathlib.PosixPath.__repr__.__class__.__name__ and pathlib.PosixPath.__str__.__class__.__name__ — both are 'function'; PosixPath is a concrete Python class for POSIX paths that inherits __repr__ and __str__ from PurePath"
  kind: python_call_eq
